Author: PORN_coin
Title: [AIRDROP][ANN][PORNX] 🌟⭐️🌟 PORNX ⚡️Lightning network⚡️ payment system 🌟⭐️🌟
Body: 2nd round of PORNX Bounty Campaign - ONLY 6 WEEKS!!!  This bounty campaign will last for 6 WEEKS ending with the ICO. PORNX team offer 1% of final token supply.  1 week - 19 May - 25 May 2 week - 26 May - 1 June 3 week - 2 June - 8 June 4 week - 9 June - 15 June 5 week - 16 June -  22 June 6 week - 23 June - 30 June   Bounty Allocation  •Signature Bounty 40% (budget will be reduced twice to 20% if number of participants will be less than 15) •Youtube/Blogging Bounty 25% (High Quality content will be accepted only) •Twitter Bounty 40%   Rules •First week of the bounty campaign will start on 19th of May, Saturday. •For any questions regarding the bounty campaign please use this thread. •We reserve our right to eliminate you if we think you haven't been honest with your work. •We reserve the right to change bounty campaign rules.   Signature Campaign  Rewards:  •Jr. Member: 1 stake per week •Member: 2 stake per week •Full Member: 3 stake per week (+1 stake for avatar) •Senior Member: 4 stakes per week (+1 stake for avatar) •Hero Member/Legendary: 5 stakes per week (+1 stake for avatar)    Signature Campaign Rules:  •Participants have to be at least Jr. Member. •Every participants must have PORNX signature and personal text. •Multiple accounts is not allowed and will be banned. •We expect you to post at least 8 constructive posts per week. •Post must be longer than 100 characters without spaces. •Off-topic posts and posts in bounty threads will not counted. •You have to keep signature, avatar and personal text till the end of the Bounty Campaign.    Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/qwKEBCfpNp38rdwy2 Spreadsheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1HdYJ8UZ_6aZ6aQrsc6yqOGQIbZSFfSDfE3DQGAWJnWs    Youtube/Blogging/Article Campaign  •You must have at least 300 organic subscribers or aticle/video should have 300 views at least. •Articles and Video should be public available till the end of token distribution. •You should have links to PORNX website and whitepaper. •Don't repost the same articles in different sources - only 1 unique article will be accepted. •Articles with bad translations will not accepted •Articles with mistakes will not accepted •Article with fake views will not accepted •Your Ethereum address have to be posted at the end of the article to be qualified. •You will get from 0 to 20 stakes, based on the quality, audience, and subjective opinion of PORNX Team    Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/PhJ7aBnpFaq9m4Lj1 Spreadsheet of accepted works: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1WSe1-mRbcfoD_JBonEFJBoypH4jnwVhKItoNs4YWgOI     Twitter Campaign  General Requerements:  •All participants must follow PORNX official Twitter account. •Your audit score must be more than 90%. •You have to have at least 500 real followers. •Your Twitter account must be 3 month older •Multiple accounts is not allowed and will be banned. •Number of followers will be fixed in the moment of registration and will not change  To be qualified for weekly reward you have to:  •Retweet at lest 5 tweets per week (or all tweets) •You have to make at least 2 own Tweets in a week about PORNX. •Only 1 Tweet per day will count. (minimum interval between tweets 10 hours) •Tweets must be in English and include ALL hashtags #PORNX #PORNX_ICO •Post the links to your Tweets\Retweets and likes before Friday 23:59 UTC.  Weekly Rewards: •   500-2000 Followers - 1 stake/week. •   2000-5000 Followers - 2 stake/week. •   5000+ Followers - 3  stake/week  •Report have to posted in this thread  till the end each Friday  23.59 UTC. •One week - one message with all your links. Don't edit your previsous reports or you will be disqualified from Bounty. •Late reports will not accepted  Form of report: Code: Week #1 (19 May - 25 May) Twitter Account link: # in spreadsheet: # of Followers: Twitts: Retweets:   Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/x4OL9SCiYwH7ILBg2 Spreadsheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1keW8DU5tOXgSSlBNvpQLBfoj2hkEjYX2Bwjhx8jpFj0

Body: Bitcoin became an innovative crypto currency, which paved the way for the rest. At present, there are several crypto-currencies that are faster, cheaper and more private, and the world reacts to them by moving their money to these more efficient networks.  Earlier in 2017, SatoshiPay announced that they would no longer use Bitcoin's block account to process payments, but would use Stellar. As the reasons indicated - faster payments and lower commission fees, as well as a "mature" and "stable" ecosystem.  A few months later, in December 2017, the popular Steam gaming platform announced that it would also move away from Bitcoin as a method of payment.  In addition, Bitcoin has lost more than 20% of its value on Christmas Eve and struggling to stay above $ 14,000.  Lightning network is a method by which Bitcoin's transaction speed can be significantly increased while processing fee will decrease.  At the moment Bitcoin has one of the slowest processing speeds among all forms of crypto online payments.  The Lightning network can provide Bitcomune with the ability to scale up to billions of transactions per day.  The Lightning network uses technology outside the network, which means that not every transaction is recorded on the blockroom. This process shortens the processing time, as well as the payment to Bitcoin miners who check the transaction.  Instead of the block system, the system includes parallel platforms that open between two parties that participate in frequent bitcoin transactions.  So, if Stephen buys a bagel from the cafe several times a month during the lunch break, he and the merchant can open a secure and individual payment channel by the Bitkoyans through the Lightning network.  If the oral agreement between the two parties comes to an end, either party may terminate the payment channel at any time, after which the remaining funds held on the channel will be returned to the owners.  In a separate balance, transactions are registered in the Lightning network, which are then stored within a separate payment channel. These transactions are recorded on the block account in two cases - when the payment terminal is opened and when it closes.

Body: In 2015, the crypto currency bitcoin faced scaling problems - the inability of the network to process more than 3-7 transactions per second. This restriction is conceptual, in other words, increasing the bandwidth in the old format - by increasing the block - can lead to a weakening of the decentralized property inherent in the crypto-currency - the absence of a single point of failure.  The community chose several ways to improve the network. Eventually, the disagreement led to the division of bitcoin into two parts: Bitcoin and Bitcoin Cash, the first of which chose scaling through the SegWit + Lightning Network. Unfortunately, bitcoin at the moment is a coin for input and output of fiat money to the crypto currency, the main transactions are exactly Bitcoin, in the more rare cases Ethereum. The bitcoin resource is limited by the number of coins, namely 21 000 000 coins, this is a programmed model that does not allow increasing the number of coins in principle. Imagine that everyone will pay bitcoin, network overload will be fatal. In addition, when carrying out large-scale ICO - and acceptance of such coins as Bitcoin and Etherium. Transaction confirmation time is increased many times, and can reach several hours. Imagine: you went to pay for a purchase in a boarding school and wait for a transaction confirmation about 3 hours, it's unthinkable   That's why companies such as X-Wall LTD conduct ICO to create a coin for payment in the local area - for example, porn sites, webcams, sex shops. And for the sustainable use of the PORN_coin coin, you need to conduct quick micro-transactions and give coins the properties of anonymity, confidentiality and security.
